    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://ontology.amt.org/im#Lead"/>
    <rdfs:label>captured by</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>Audit/provenance metadata only — NOT a UFO relator participant or external dependence. Identifies the BoothStaff who operated the scanner when known. The Lead's existence does not require BoothStaff to be identified (cardinality 0..1), and the Lead carries no information about the BoothStaff beyond identity reference.</rdfs:comment>
